= Training Session 2 Overview

#info-box[
  *Assignment Details:*
  - *Total Questions:* 18
  - *Time Limit:* 36 minutes (strictly timed)
  - *Average Pace:* 2 minutes per question
  - *Topic:* Number Properties & Arithmetic
  - *Assign After:* Lesson B
  - *Review In:* Lesson C
]

#warning-box[
  *Instructions for Student:*
  1. Find a quiet place with no distractions
  2. Set a timer for 36 minutes
  3. Do NOT pause the timer for any reason
  4. Complete all questions in order
  5. Mark any questions you found difficult
  6. Record your time if you finish early
]

#tip-box[
  *Training 2 Focus:*

  This training builds on Training 1 with:
  - Slightly increased difficulty
  - More emphasis on areas where Training 1 showed weakness
  - More complex applications of concepts
  - Questions requiring multiple concepts
]

